{"word":"ἀφνειός","slug":"ἀφνειός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀφνειός</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἄφενος'><el>ἄφενος</el></a>\n<p/><i>rich, wealthy</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>; <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <el>ἀφνειὸς βιότοιο</el> <i>rich in</i> substance, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>; <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b>; <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b><p/>"}]}